@startuml sequence_followups
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Ask - Follow-up chips

participant "AskModePage" as UI
participant "POST /api/ask" as API
participant "IChatClient" as CC

... streaming answer + citations ...
API -> CC: non-stream chat for 3 followups
CC --> API: JSON ["q1","q2","q3"]
API --> UI: event: followups
UI -> UI: render 3 FollowUpChip
API --> UI: event: done

actor User
User -> UI: tap "Draft pitch to Sarah"
UI -> UI: submit("Draft pitch to Sarah")

@enduml
